subject: Dog Sledding
Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race (Alaska)
lead_paragraph: Hundreds of sled dogs and thousands of fans lined up in Anchorage for the ceremonial start of the 1,100-mile Iditarod Trail Sled Dog Race.
